CONNECTION 2: ARNOLD TONGUES & DEVIL'S STAIRCASE
======================================================================

Arnold tongues in the circle map x_{n+1} = x_n + О© - (K/2ПЂ)sin(2ПЂx_n)
lock onto rational rotation numbers p/q. The widths of tongues follow
a Stern-Brocot/Farey structure with Fibonacci rationals (F_n/F_{n+1})
having the NARROWEST tongues вЂ” hardest to lock.

Mapping tournament eigenvalues to rotation numbers:

