The LARGEST Q_k dominates: Q_1/ОЈQ в†’ 0.81 в‰€ 1-1/(2П†ВІ)
This means the 'devil's staircase' has a GIANT first step
of height 81%, with remaining 19% spread across m-1 modes.
In Arnold tongue language: the fundamental mode is at the
