This is the first Fourier coefficient of the square wave!
F_m(2ПЂ/p) / mВІ в†’ sincВІ(1/2) = (sin(ПЂ/2)/(ПЂ/2))ВІ = 4/ПЂВІ

And from the bulk: ОЈQ = m(m+1)/2, so bulk total = m(m+1)/2 - Q_1
