These are DIFFERENT constants! The limit is 8/ПЂВІ, NOT golden-ratio related.
The near-coincidence (0.8106 vs 0.8090) is explained by 8/ПЂВІ - (1-1/(2П†ВІ))
= 0.001552 в‰€ 1/600.

======================================================================
SYNTHESIS: THE FIBONACCI-FOURIER DUALITY
